Hi. My name is Ismael.

I have experience with a wide range of programming languages and tools including Java, Python, JavaScript, HTML, React, Bootstrap, Flutter, and Android development.

Throughout my career, I have worked on a number of exciting projects that have allowed me to hone my skills and showcase my creativity. One of my most notable projects is VINScanner, an Android app for scanning VINs to get vehicle information and recall history. This app has been downloaded by thousands of users and has received positive reviews for its ease of use and accuracy.

In addition to VINScanner, I have also developed Trivial Trivia, a Flutter trivia app with leaderboards, follow lists, a variety of game modes including a Daily Challenge option which gives very hard questions in a tight timeframe as well as an option for custom games for specific categories of questions and optional time limits. This project allowed me to experiment with new tools and technologies while creating a fun and engaging user experience.

Another one of my projects is ChatterBox, a simple messaging app that enables users to communicate with each other in real-time. This project was a great way for me to explore the world of mobile app development and learn more about user interface design and user experience.

All of my projects can be found on my Github page at https://github.com/Ismael-Deka. I am always looking for new and exciting opportunities to expand my skillset and take on new challenges. If you are interested in working with me or learning more about my experience, feel free to reach out to me. I look forward to hearing from you!
); } export default HomePage;
